# Encrypted Bank

A terminal-based tool for secure financial transactions, built with *************.

## Features

-   Secure Bank-to-Bank ACH Transfer
-   Cash-to-Bitcoin conversion with a generated barcode
-   Multi-method Deposit portal
-   Real-time "Dirty to Clean" transaction monitoring terminal

## Disclaimer

**This tool is for educational and entertainment purposes only. It is a simulation and does not perform any real financial transactions or connect to any banking networks. Use it ethically and responsibly.**

## Installation on Kali Linux

1.  Clone the repository:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/encrypted-bank.git
    cd encrypted-bank
    ```

2.  Install the required dependencies:
    ```bash
    pip3 install -r requirements.txt
    ```

3.  Make the script executable:
    ```bash
    chmod +x eb.py
    ```

